r is run by a separate company, the Mirage fixed the issue by compensating me the difference off my bill for other hotel charges. Again, good service - I got my money back.But I wont be going back to the Revolution. The people in there are the bottom feeders.RestaurantsWe tried the Japonaise - the sushi was fanstastic and priced very reasonably. $7 per order.We also tried the Fin - very good as always. Make sure you grab reservations for them.SpaThe salon did a great job for me, and also the spa - desert stone massage was very nice.	
