!!Las Vegas Monorail: Very convenient and a decent price!! Took it to both ends of the strip.Shopping: Fashion Show Mall - tonnes of great stores that are reasonably priced, great locationMiracle Mile Mall - very similar to Fashion Show Mall, great storesPrimm Outlets - nice mall but had the same stores as the outlets in VegasVegas Premium Outlets - good selection of stores, convenient location** Just an FYI - watch out for the Taxi Cab drivers!! They have zero patience for people and if they don't feel they are making enough money for driving you - they will not take you. I was actually left standing there as the cab drove away with the door openwhen I told him where I wanted to go. After that experience I took every other mode of transportation!! To sum it up....EXCELLENT trip to Vegas and the hotel was beautiful!!	
