O FUN...if you can get in! We 3 girls got bracelets from a guy at the door &amp; walked right in (well, almost...just a 10 min. wait). It was a Tuesday night, though - they may not be so generous on weekends. Still, it was packed with fun people &amp; a great DJ! - If you're going during the week &amp; you want to go to a club or see a show, check on the &quot;dark&quot; days beforehand. The things you want to see might be closed on random weeknights!Overall, Vegas is hot, crowded, expensive...but if you let loose &amp; know what to expect you will have a FANTASTIC time! Can't wait to go back.	
