 comparable to Dicks Last Resort. Everywhere else we ate was great. BLT Burger is really good but a little pricy. We also ate at Cal. Pizza Kitchen and got better service at both. The Mirage provided our wedding cake &amp; it was AMAZING. Thanks to Erin D. Just what I wanted and it was huge, but still Stack managed to tell us that they had no idea where it was. How you could lose a cake that big was beyond me, but they did. Everywhere else inside Mirage service was great! Stack is owned by The Lightgroup so Mirage is not responsible for them. We didn't finish all the cake so Mirage sent us a fridge to store it in and even sent us plates later so we could share with family and friends. Also got my wedding hair done at Kim Vo and they were also amazing. I have really long, thick hair &amp; my updo was done in under an hour. Overall it was a great trip besides our experience at Stack. The location is great for the strip, the casino is great, and the updates were a good change. Won pretty big &amp; Can't wait to go back. Love ya LV!!	
